+-------------------------[ Option Select Menu: ]------------------------+  

                                                         
        You use the ¥F1¥ - ¥F4¥ keys to select the various options.     
    
                ¥F1¥ You can choose the number of players      
            ¥F2¥ You can choose between the various game types 
           ¥F3¥ You can choose between 1 up to 1o laps per race 
     ¥F4¥ When you are happy with your selections this will begin the  
                  game.You can choose one of the tracks. 
 

+---------------------[ How to control your car : ]----------------------+

          
                          Joystick Controls:                              
                       +----------------------+
                          Fire = Accelerate                            
                          Left = Steer Left                            
                          Right = Steer Right                          


                          Keyboard controls:                          
                       +----------------------+

                        - Blue Car:                           
                          Left Shift = Accelerate
                          Left alt = Steer left  
                          Left Amiga = Steer right 

                        - Green Car (Two Megs Only):
                          Right Shift = Acclerate 
                          Right Amiga = Steer Left
                          Right Alt = Steer Right                 


                         In game key controls: 
                       +----------------------+
                          P = Game Pause
                          Q = Quits current race and if all human players
                          have finished it finishes the computer cars
                          automatically.

